name: Virtual Photography #5 (The New META'cis Pt. #1)
description: 'We Focus And Invest On Ventures And Projects Related To Blockchain Tech And Crypto Assets.' Token Angels has become a notable collector in what arguably could be the nexus point of modern art history. As Bitcoin changed the whole world's perception of where asset classes could exist, so too could the acceptance of rareified digital art be heralded as a new dawn of modern art markets and collectability. As I perceive Token Angels as one of the new 'Meta'cis,' a techno-wordplay off of the old Renaissance style of patronage by the Medici family....a whole new support for arts in a whole new world of finance is just beginning. - Robness(L.A. born and raised, beach bum for life) XOXO
collection_description: SuperRare makes it easy to create, sell, and collect rare digital art. SuperRare's smart contract platform allows artists to release limited-edition digital artwork tracked on the blockchain, making the pieces rare, verified, and collectible. Filter the crypto art world's best selling works by artist name, creation type, and year of birth on OpenSea.
